    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be posting this, but it\u2019s time for my absolute pride and joy to find a new home. I have babied this beauty since the moment I got it\u2014we're talking garage-kept, hand-washed, and treated like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly stunning condition, looking and smelling just like it did on the showroom floor. Every time I get behind the wheel, it puts a massive smile on my face, and I know it\u2019ll do the same for you. It\u2019s rare to find one kept this clean, so come on over, let\u2019s have a chat, and you can see for yourself how special she is!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
