      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 in Carbon Black. This isn't your typical high-mileage driver; we\u2019ve executed a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan systems components and a full subframe reinforcement with TMS plates to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The S54 powerplant maintains factory-spec compression across all six cylinders, delivering a linear torque curve that pulls relentlessly to the 8,000 RPM redline. Suspension has been dialed in with Ohlins Road & Track coilovers, offering surgical turn-in precision without sacrificing chassis composure. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history that reads like a workshop manual. Truly a turn-key apex predator for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint. Flawless. Showroom ready. Zero issues. Priced to move today. Don't wait.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
