      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a real head-turner. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it truly shows\u2014it\u2019s in that rare, showroom-fresh condition that\u2019s getting harder to find. Whether you\u2019re cruising on the weekend or just want something that feels brand new every time you hop in, this is the one. It runs like a clock and looks even better in person. Come say hi and see for yourself why I love it so much!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This S54 powerplant is a mechanical symphony, benefiting from a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan systems and upgraded rod bearings for absolute peace of mind. The chassis is rock-solid, featuring a proactive rear subframe reinforcement with TMS plates\u2014essential for maintaining structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. Performance is sharpened by a corner-balanced Bilstein PSS10 suspension and a lightweight flywheel that allows the revs to climb with surgical precision. The Getrag 6-speed gearbox is tight, throwing into gear with mechanical finality. Inside, the Nappa leather remains supple, showing zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key collector-grade example for the purist who demands peak rotational mass efficiency and a perfect power-to-weight ratio.",
